<html><p>The <a href="https://marketplace.microfocus.com/itom/content/optic-data-lake-management-pack">OPTIC Data Lake Management Pack</a>, which you can download from ITOM Marketplace, discovers and monitors key areas of the OPTIC Data Lake on-premises including the data flow, agent metric collection, and basic Kubernetes and Vertica availability.</p>

<p>This content monitors:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Kubernetes pods are running and nodes are ready.</li>
	<li>Vertica availability, including the status of the Vertica database cluster nodes.</li>
	<li>Key Agent Metric Collector metrics.</li>
	<li>OPTIC DL data flow from the HTTP Receiver through the Message Bus for key topics and into in the Vertica raw tables and hourly/daily aggregation for key tables, and hourly/daily aggregation for key tables representative of these data sources: Operations Agent, SiteScope, BPM, OBM events.</li>
</ul>

<p>You can optionally extend the infrastructure monitoring by adding the following:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Install SiteScope and deploy the Vertica solution template for more extensive Vertica monitoring.</li>
	<li>Deploy either SiteScope or an OBM Management Pack for discovery and monitoring of the PostgreSQL or Oracle RDBMS used by the Operations Bridge suite.</li>
	<li>Install the CDF certificate expiry monitoring content pack that is bundled with the <a href="https://marketplace.microfocus.com/itom/content/opsbridge-container-deployment-troubleshooting-toolkit">OpsBridge Container Deployment Troubleshooting Toolkit</a> on ITOM Marketplace.</li>
</ul>

